#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.dragonplayer.appdata.xml:12
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Dragon Player is a multimedia player where the focus is on simplicity, "
#| "instead of features. Dragon Player does one thing, and only one thing, "
#| "which is playing multimedia files. Its simple interface is designed not "
#| "to get in your way and instead empower you to simply play multimedia "
#| "files."
msgid ""
"Dragon Player is a video player focusing on simplicity instead of features. "
"Its easy-to-use interface is designed to get out of your way and simply play "
"your video files and streams."
msgstr ""
"Dragon Player इति बहुमाध्यमप्लेयरः यत्र सरलतायाः विषये ध्यानं भवति, विशेषतानां स्थाने । "
"Dragon Player एकं कार्यं करोति, केवलं एकं कार्यं च, यत् बहुमाध्यमसञ्चिकाः क्रीडति । अस्य "
"सरलं अन्तरफलकं भवतः मार्गे न प्रविष्टुं विनिर्मितम् अस्ति तथा च तस्य स्थाने केवलं "
"बहुमाध्यमसञ्चिकाः वादयितुं सशक्तं करोति ।"

